high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the coffee table.
Pick the laptop from the coffee table.
Turn left and walk towards the bed.
Place the laptop on the bed.
anns.task_desc: To place the laptop on the bed.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the doorway, then hang a right, turn to the dresser table to your right and go to the coffee table
Pick up the laptop on the coffee table
Turn left and walk past the dresser table and hang a left and walk to the bedroom on your left
Put the laptop on the bed
Exit from the room turn right go straight again turn right to the coffee table
Pick the laptop from the coffee table
Turn left walk back to the bed
Place the laptop on the bed
anns.task_desc: Pick the laptop from the coffee table and place it on the bed
